50|$|CIPPIC was {{initially}} {{founded on a}} grant from an Amazon.com <b>cy-près</b> fund that was matched by the Ontario Research Network for Electronic Commerce. In 2007, it received a major donation from professors Robert J. Glushko and Pamela Samuelson which ensured that CIPPIC {{would be able to}} continue its operations. CIPPIC continues to operate through donations and the support of the University of Ottawa.|$|E
